{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act43side", "eventName": "紅絲絨", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "AD-2", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "排演一齣悲劇", "storyInfo": "拍攝現場，謝莉陷入幻覺將自己置於險境，關鍵時刻被盧西恩所救。藉由此次意外，盧西恩打聽出了五年前的劇組事故——年輕女演員勞拉命殞片場。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g2_setting_rooftop", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 0.0, "type": "bg", "from": 0.0, "to": 0.3}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 1.07, "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-70", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 1.07, "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-60", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 1.3, "yScaleTo": 1.3, "duration": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.1, "block": "false", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.1, "block": "true", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$distressed_intro", "key": "$distressed_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1", "focus": "r", "posfrom": "0,-60", "posto": "0,-60"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 1.07}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "忘記不幸遇害的兄長，跟我私奔吧，杜邦夫人！", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#5$1", "focus": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-70"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 1.07}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "清醒一點，第二個洛克菲勒！", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也聽到了那個信使說的，根本不存在什麼“杜邦夫人”，什麼高貴、優雅、知性……所有我身上你們所愛的東西都是無根的浮萍……", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#4$1", "focus": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-70"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 1.07}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不配成為你們兄弟三人中任何一人的妻子。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1", "focus": "r", "posfrom": "0,-60", "posto": "0,-60"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 1.07}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我愛你，就算你不姓杜邦我也依然愛你！", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1", "focus": "r", "posfrom": "0,-60", "posto": "0,-60"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 1.07}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是你的兄長，那個死掉的傢伙一直在利用你，你被蒙在鼓裡，你也是受害者，你又何苦為此自責？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#4$1", "focus": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-70"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 1.07}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是……", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#6$1", "focus": "r", "posfrom": "0,-60", "posto": "0,-60"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 1.07}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#4$1", "focus": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-70"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 1.07}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在會客廳擠滿了前來弔唁的賓客，雖然“杜邦”只是一個虛名，但於情於理我都不應該當著他們的面離開……", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1", "focus": "r", "posfrom": "0,-60", "posto": "0,-60"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 1.07}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有辦法能讓我們現在就離開宅邸，從此再也不理會家族紛爭。", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#6$1", "focus": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-70"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 1.07}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這要如何做到？", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1", "focus": "r", "posfrom": "0,-60", "posto": "0,-60"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 1.07}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你忘記了？我是一名軍人，親愛的。", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看！", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#3$1", "focus": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-70"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 1.07}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這、這是……", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1", "focus": "r", "posfrom": "0,-60", "posto": "0,-60"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 1.07}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在這座宅邸的儲藏室蒐集了材料，製作了這條鋼索……抓緊吊纜，我們就能從這個露台直接飛躍花園，抵達屋後的森林。", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跟我走吧，去一個不在乎財富和階級的地方！", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 0.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 5.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "action": "jump", "posto": "0,-300", "power": 50.0, "times": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "action": "jump", "posto": "0,-300", "power": 50.0, "times": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sldrsldng", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，軍人先生，你的方法還是太野蠻了！", "name": "米蘭妮"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萬一滑輪卡住，我們會懸掛在半空中好幾個小時，直到有人發現我們……或者繩索斷裂直接墜入森林……", "name": "米蘭妮"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相信我，裝置非常安全。我不會讓你受傷的，親愛的。", "name": "邁克爾"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "洛克菲勒，這是真、真的嗎？我、我覺得我快掉下去了——", "name": "米蘭妮"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wiatear"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 10.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$plot_intro", "key": "$plot_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊——！", "name": "謝莉"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "text": "鋼索、吊纜、懸掛、墜落。", "x": 200.0, "y": 300.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 900.0, "duration": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st3", "text": "墜落。", "x": 307.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 900.0, "duration": 8.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st4", "text": "墜落。", "x": 307.0, "y": 410.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 900.0, "duration": 15.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wiatear_break"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st3"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st4"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$glass", "delay": 0.5}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_ambulancewhistle", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“有人掉下來了！快！快叫救護車！滿地都是血……謝莉！你還愣在這裡做什麼！”"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "脊背被寒意攫住，手指連動也不能動，神經也跟隨繩索緩慢斷裂的聲音不斷受到拉扯。"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 5.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“到底是怎麼回事……”"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“所以，劇組的結論就是，她的死只是鋼絲年久老舊造成的意外？就這樣輕描淡寫地解決了？這是死了一個人啊！”"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不像……對……兩起事故一點都不像。道爾頓死於刀下，而五年前的演員死於墜亡。"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wiatear"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咯吱。咯吱。不祥的斷裂聲再次響起。在哪裡？究竟在哪裡？"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……謝莉，謝莉！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "發什麼呆啊，快點離開那裡，貨箱要掉下來了！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 0.0, "type": "bg", "from": 0.0, "to": 0.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g3_filmset", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "掉……掉下來？", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝莉僵在原地，呆板地抬頭。"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 2.0, "vibrato": 5.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodenladder"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她看著吊在空中的貨箱離頭頂越來越近，彷彿吊在空中的是自己，而她即將墜落。"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在貨箱佔據謝莉視野的下一秒，影子出現在她的身旁，一雙有力的手握住她的手臂。"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovementsp"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝莉感到一陣天旋地轉，回過神時她已離開了原來的位置，安穩落在拍攝現場的另一邊。"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1", "duration": 1.0, "posfrom": "-100,0", "posto": "-100,0"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩……謝、謝謝你。", "name": "謝莉"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可以放手了。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "posfrom": "-100,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，對不起。", "name": "謝莉"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是說你。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫伊拉，你是叫這個名字吧……可以放手了。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好……好。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#4$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝莉這才看到，連接著貨箱的繩索被小個子的道具師死死地拉在手上，她的手臂在顫抖，臉也憋得通紅。"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到盧西恩重複了一遍，她才慢慢地鬆開手。"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 15.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_container_smash", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的神經太緊繃了。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這、這是我作為道具組長的職責。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這到底是怎麼回事……", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1847_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼回事，我還想問你呢，怎麼回事？", "name": "工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1847_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些貨箱確實使用好幾年了，需要重新檢查一遍以防繩索再次鬆脫，但你——", "name": "工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1847_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你真的是瘋了，謝莉！", "name": "工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1847_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫名其妙驚叫出聲，打斷了拍攝不說，連危險逼近了都不知道躲開嗎？", "name": "工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1847_1#1$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你難道是第一次看劇組拍吊鋼絲嗎？嚇成這樣！", "name": "工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1847_1#1$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……米蘭妮和邁克爾的樣子，讓我想起了五年前那個墜落的——", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝莉，你先下去休息吧，別干擾劇組正常拍攝。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4198_christ_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（跳過道具箱）", "name": "Miss.Christine"}, "figure_art": "avg_4198_christ_1#2$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4198_christ_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_MCcat_3"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（貼近盧西恩）", "name": "Miss.Christine"}, "figure_art": "avg_4198_christ_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒、沒什麼，這個神秘的黑傢伙剛剛在那邊亂竄，我被嚇到了……", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起，請繼續拍攝吧。", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4198_christ_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "Miss.Christine"}, "figure_art": "avg_4198_christ_1#7$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_MCcat_4"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（不滿地甩動雙尾）", "name": "Miss.Christine"}, "figure_art": "avg_4198_christ_1#7$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g3_filmset", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果仔細看……謝莉長得也不差，就是總愛大驚小怪的，讓人心裡發毛。", "name": "邁克爾"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛那場戲被打斷真可惜，我的情緒正漸入佳境……", "name": "邁克爾"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“漸入佳境”？", "name": "米蘭妮"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邁克爾，你要感謝那位統籌小姐。要不是她中斷拍攝，下一秒我就要罵出口了。", "name": "米蘭妮"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "台詞、身形、情感……一無是處，整整兩個月的拍攝，到現在你的表現甚至沒有那位只演了一場戲的新人亮眼。", "name": "米蘭妮"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我告訴過你，別把私生活的那一套帶進拍攝裡，現在看來，根本問題在於格蕾塔看錯人了。", "name": "米蘭妮"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她根本不該找只靠一對紅耳朵就接到戲的偶像派擔任主角，還一人分飾三角。", "name": "米蘭妮"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "邁克爾"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您說得對。", "name": "邁克爾"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，怎麼一副無精打采的樣子？", "name": "米蘭妮"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "平時這個時候，你早就開始用油腔滑調的語氣為自己辯解了。", "name": "米蘭妮"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不就是因為想起可憐的老道爾頓了嗎……", "name": "邁克爾"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有您資深，進組經驗也不夠豐富。剛剛被謝莉的意外影響，現在又有點心神不寧。", "name": "邁克爾"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "專業一點。", "name": "米蘭妮"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "意外、失敗、負面評價……要是會被這些小事影響到表演的狀態，根本沒辦法在藍卡塢待下去。", "name": "米蘭妮"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，我的抗壓能力還不夠強，得向您多多請教……", "name": "邁克爾"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說瑪麗安娜女士憑一部二十八天拍成的影片包攬藍卡塢電影節各類獎項時，您就在她的身後？", "name": "邁克爾"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "米蘭妮"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算顆粒無收，被報紙和記者冷嘲熱諷，您還是照常回到劇組完成了當天的拍攝。", "name": "邁克爾"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是我必須跟這樣璀璨奪目的演員競爭，可能早就不拍戲了……", "name": "邁克爾"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這是什麼意思？", "name": "米蘭妮"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……哦！", "name": "邁克爾"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不不不，您誤會了，我只是想瞭解您面對道爾頓的意外能保持鎮定的秘訣，絕對沒有別的意思！", "name": "邁克爾"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "秘訣？沒有什麼秘訣，只是因為我並不熟悉道爾頓，也與那起事故毫無關係。", "name": "米蘭妮"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反倒是你。", "name": "米蘭妮"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你為他心神不寧那麼久，難道他的死與你有關？", "name": "米蘭妮"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "邁克爾"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g7_mobileplotstreet_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道這一切真的只是巧合？", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道只是我的疑心病太重？", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道我真的應該去看一下心理醫生？", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Miss.Christine不該成為你的藉口。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰！", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝莉小姐，Miss.Christine當時並沒有出現在你所說的位置，更不會亂竄驚嚇到你。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩，請你代替我向你的同伴說聲抱歉吧。", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會的。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，你恐懼的究竟是什麼？", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你應該問五年前劇組發生意外後，還有什麼不令我恐懼。", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的眼神寫滿了好奇。", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可以告訴你——其實本來也不是什麼秘密，打聽一下就能知道。", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個發生意外的女孩，叫勞拉。", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她是一個初到藍卡塢的新人演員，被格蕾塔女士招募進組，對自己的工作熱情得過分，但完全不懂行業的規矩。", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "道爾頓當時已經染上酒癮，但人氣未減。為了教訓一下不禮貌的後輩，他故意臨時加戲，讓小演員在鋼絲上吊了六七個小時。", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒想到裝置老舊導致繩索鬆脫……那名演員墜落身亡。", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下一秒，血液從那名演員身下蔓延開，就像那天道爾頓的樣子……", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩看向謝莉的手臂，潛意識的不安教唆她對自己的身體行兇，血痕遍布。"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝莉立即拉下捲在手臂上的袖子，神色不安。"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會解決自己的問題。", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你低估了所謂的“問題”。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它會出現得越來越頻繁，原本只是類似的聲響才會引發幻覺，而現在哪怕只是拖動椅子，也會把你拉回那段過去。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝你的關心，盧西恩“醫生”。", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和我腦中邪惡的小聲響已經相處了五年，我瞭解它們。", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只能跟它們賽跑，在恐懼和非理性徹底佔據我的大腦之前，盡可能多做些什麼。", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許道爾頓的死真的是一個意外，但我需要排除所有風險和威脅，避免五年前的事再次上演。", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕那些威脅來自於劇組的發起者……", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還有別的顧慮。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格蕾塔對我隱瞞了什麼。", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們共用一個辦公室，移動地塊開出藍卡塢主城區前，我在她桌上發現一份奇怪的文件，正想打開的時候被她攔下。", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謎題越來越多，而我跟那些相熟的成員分享著一段不堪的回憶，無法保持坦誠。", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在還有惱人的聲音和幻覺打斷我的思緒……", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "疼痛是一種緩解方法。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說……什麼？", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說，“疼痛”。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它無法解決你的幻覺和歇斯底里，但能為你提供喘息的機會，讓你完成自己真正想做的事，解開未知的謎題。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些難以分辨真假的聲音和影子會藏在細小的夾縫中，在你試圖找回自我的時候阻止你，擾亂你……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "疼痛是用來對抗它們的方法，只不過指甲的硬度可能不夠。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "筆尖、刀鋒……只要用力得當，任何銳利的人造物品都能為你提供幫助。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "舌頭、手背、腿根……這些部位對疼痛更加敏感。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……真是個奇怪的人，但你似乎很瞭解幻覺。", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你曾經用這種方法讓自己鎮靜下來？", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你到底是什麼人？", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_RL_castlehall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$chenandwei_intro", "key": "$chenandwei_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "疼痛是一種緩解方式。"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "古怪的低語、可怕的景象……"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是和謝莉不同，他需要解決的問題，並非對這些事物的恐懼，而是，渴望。"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 2.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩還沒歸還源石唱片機？", "name": "劇團成員A"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還沒。", "name": "劇團成員B"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他應該也很著急吧，“白英花”不是說他最近焦慮得徹夜難眠嗎？", "name": "劇團成員B"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "狂喜和狂悲都太表象了，他體會不到更複雜更極端的情感，自然也就沒辦法突破演技的瓶頸……", "name": "劇團成員B"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他還那麼年輕，急什麼？", "name": "劇團成員A"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩已經加入劇團六七年了吧，起初那麼被看好，擁有最動人的歌聲，接受劇團長的親自教導……", "name": "劇團成員B"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好不容易擁有了當主角的機會，現在排練卻遇到了瓶頸。", "name": "劇團成員B"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他把那幾張唱片多聽幾遍，也解決不了問題啊！", "name": "劇團成員A"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1832_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_recordplayer_smash", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1832_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1832_1#2$1"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1832_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "情感是演員的武器。那麼第一步，你需要理解它們。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1832_1#1$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師說，狂喜和狂悲都只是表象，形似的模仿只會讓你喪失對更複雜情感的感知。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1832_1#1$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1832_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是要怎麼……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1832_1#5$1"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1832_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "絕望，真正的絕望會讓你失去最珍視之物，同時為你打開一扇新的門……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1832_1#2$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1832_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你將聆聽一切你不曾聆聽之低語，你將目睹一切你不曾目睹之景象，你將感悟一切你不曾感悟之情感……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1832_1#3$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你將成為，萬物的明鏡，戲劇本身。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1832_1#3$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1832_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "像這樣——", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1832_1#7$1"}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.3, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$knifegore", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1832_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳，咳咳——", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1832_1#5$1"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩毀掉了自己的歌喉。"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "源石結晶在一瞬間灌入傷口，疼痛與絕望將他淹沒。"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1833_1#6$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "血……", "name": "沉淵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1833_1#6$1"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1832_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "痛……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1832_1#5$1"}, {"id": 415, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1833_1#7$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1833_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩，別怕，我在這裡！", "name": "沉淵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1833_1#7$1"}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到底發生什麼事情了？", "name": "沉淵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1833_1#7$1"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1832_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（嘶啞的嗚咽）", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1832_1#5$1"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1832_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（變化的聲線）原來……這就是……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1832_1#9$1"}, {"id": 425, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1833_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩，是你自己把自己弄成這樣的？", "name": "沉淵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1833_1#2$1"}, {"id": 427, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1833_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "沉淵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1833_1#4$1"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1833_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還記得我之前的那次演出……或者說刺殺嗎？", "name": "沉淵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1833_1#1$1"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我失敗了。他們說，我是個可悲的懦夫。", "name": "沉淵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1833_1#1$1"}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩，我已經不再是備受期待的藝術之子，我也不在乎那些孤立與嘲笑，因為我的心在那場演出後就已經不在劇團了……", "name": "沉淵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1833_1#1$1"}, {"id": 433, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我還是留下來了……我們來自同個家鄉，我們是……朋友。", "name": "沉淵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1833_1#1$1"}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你答應過我，不會像他們那樣……", "name": "沉淵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1833_1#1$1"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1832_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師的話……是對的……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1832_1#9$1"}, {"id": 437, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1833_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……", "name": "沉淵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1833_1#1$1"}, {"id": 439, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我害怕……這座劇團，還有現在的你。", "name": "沉淵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1833_1#1$1"}, {"id": 440, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 2.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g7_mobileplotstreet_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之，它會比你想像中的更有效。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 452, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 453, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}, {"id": 454, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 455, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望我永遠用不到你教我的“小技巧”。", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}, {"id": 456, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 457, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 458, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 459, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 460, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 461, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 462, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}